{"tid":2168371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"物流署向社署提供最多外購口罩　警獲 347 萬 CSI 口罩冠絕各部門","createTime":"2020-08-21T17:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T17:19:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"97aad7f8486a8c93704be5335ce4de9230215a54","tid":2168371,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"政府今日向立法會提交個人防護裝備報告，透露在 1 月至 7 月期間，物流署共購入約 3 億 2800 萬個口罩。懲教署亦生產了約 2300 萬個 CSI 口罩。物流署亦同時購入其他防護裝備如 N95 呼吸器、面罩、全身保護服等，總共支出約 13 億元。而獲發最多採購口罩的是社會福利署，逾 1300 萬個；警務處則獲發最多 CSI 口罩，約為 347 萬個。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E7%BD%B2%E5%90%91%E7%A4%BE%E7%BD%B2%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%BC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E8%AD%A6%E7%8D%B2-347-%E8%90%AC-csi-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%86%A0%E7%B5%95%E5%90%84%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25B5%2581%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%258D%25B2-347-%25E8%2590%25AC-csi-%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%2590%2584%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2596%2580%2F&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=3294c896\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25B5%2581%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%258D%25B2-347-%25E8%2590%25AC-csi-%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%2590%2584%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%25